params.amountIn: The exact amount of DAI that will be swapped for WETH9.
params.buyToken: The token address when recieving in the swap
params.router: Flag for determing Uniswap or Sushiswap router

swapUni(uint256,address,address,uint16).notice: swapExactInputSingle swaps a fixed amount of DAI for a maximum possible amount of WETH9 using the DAI/WETH9 0.3% pool by calling `exactInputSingle` in the swap router.
